ode\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=''3| 2011\n| ''[[Underworld: Endless War]]''\n| [[Selene (Underworld)|Selene]]\n| Voice\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2012\n| ''[[Contraband (2012 film)|Contraband]]''\n| Kate Farraday\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Underworld: Awakening]]''\n| [[Selene (Underworld)|Selene]]\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Total Recall (2012 film)|Total Recall]]''\n| Lori Quaid\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[The Trials of Cate McCall]]''\n| Cate McCall\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2014\n| ''[[Stonehearst Asylum]]''\n| Eliza Graves\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Face of an Angel]]''\n| Simone Ford\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Absolutely Anything]]''\n| Catherine West\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2016\n| ''[[Love & Friendship]]''\n| Lady Susan Vernon\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Disappointments Room]]''\n| Dana\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Underworld: Blood Wars]]''\n| [[Selene (Underworld)|Selene]]\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[The Only Living Boy in New York (film)|The Only Living Boy in New York]]''\n| Johanna\n|\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Farming (film)|Farming]]''\n| Ingrid Carpenter\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[El Tonto]]''\n| TBA\n| Post-production\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Jolt (film)|Jolt]]''\n| Lindy\n| Post-production\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1991\n| ''[[Devices and Desires]]''\n| Young Alice Mair (voice)\n| [[Miniseries]]; episode 2\n|-\n| 1991\n| ''[[Mary Lindell#Film and television|One Against the Wind]]''\n| Barbe Lindell\n| Television film\n|-\n| 1992\n| ''Rachel's Dream''\n| Rachel\n| Short\n|-\n| 1993\n| ''[[Anna Lee (TV series)|Anna Lee]]''\n| Thea Hahn\n| [[Television pilot|Pilot]] film: \"Headcase\"\n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[Emma (1996 TV film)|Emma]]''\n| [[Emma Woodhouse]]\n| Television film\n|-\n| 1998\n| ''[[Alice through the Looking Glass (1998 film)|Alice through the Looking Glass]]''\n| [[Alice (Alice's Adventures in Wonderland)|Alice]]\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[The Widow (TV series)|The Widow]]''<ref nam