-Claude Gahd Dam]]\n| ''Underworld: Awakening''\n| {{won}}\n|<ref name=\"china\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2016\n| [[Gotham Awards]]\n| [[Gotham Independent Film Awards 2016#Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''Love & Friendship''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Awards|Critics Choice Awards]]\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Actress in a Comedy|Best Actress in a Comedy]]\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2017\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[London Critics Circle]]\n| [[London Film Critics' Circle Award for Actress of the Year]]\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| [[London Film Critics Circle Award for British Actress of the Year]]\n| {{won}}\n|\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Wikiquote}}\n{{commons category|Kate Beckinsale}}\n* {{IMDb name|id=0000295}}\n* {{Tcmdb name}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/individual/325721 |title=Beckinsale, Kate |publisher=[[British Film Institute]] Film & TV Database <!-- |accessdate=19 May 2012 -->}}\n* {{AllRovi person|4911|Kate Beckinsale}}\n* {{people.com|kate_beckinsale|Kate Beckinsale}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Awards for Kate Beckinsale\n|list =\n{{London Film Critics Circle Award for British Actress of the Year}}\n{{London Film Critics Circle Award for British Supporting Actress of the Year}}\n}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Beckinsale, Kate}}\n[[Category:1973 births]]\n[[Category:Actresses from London]]\n[[Category:Alumni of New College, Oxford]]\n[[Category:English expatriates in the United States]]\n[[Category:English film actresses]]\n[[Category:English people of Burmese descent]]\n[[Category:English television actresses]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People educated at Godolphin and Latymer School]]\n[[Category:People from Chiswick]]\n[[Category:20th-century English actresses]]\n[[Category:21st-century English actresses]]\n[[Category:English stage actresses]]\n[[Category:English radio actresses]]\n[[Category:English voice actresses]]\n[[Category:Engli