bie|last=Lord|title=Texas shooting: Who is Dimitrios Pagourtzis, suspect in the Santa Fe High School attack?|work=[[The Atlanta Journal-Constitution]]|accessdate=May 18, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519013150/https://www.ajc.com/news/national/texas-shooting-who-dimitrios-pagourtzis-suspect-the-santa-high-school-attack/TgsQw37PdCk3GM8QuLvcfI/|archive-date=May 19, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AMarch4OurLivesTweet\">{{cite news|last1=Zwirz|first1=Elizabeth|title=Parkland students react to Texas school shooting: 'Santa Fe High, you didn't deserve this'|url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2018/05/18/parkland-students-react-to-texas-school-shooting-santa-fe-high-didnt-deserve-this.html|work=[[Fox News]]|accessdate=May 19, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519002720/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2018/05/18/parkland-students-react-to-texas-school-shooting-santa-fe-high-didnt-deserve-this.html|archive-date=May 19, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all|date=May 18, 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"APNews\">{{cite news|title=Gunman blasted through door, lingered for about 30 minutes| url=https://www.apnews.com/e8a26b081e2a4206978f750fcdf20a42|first1=Paul J.|last1=Weber| first2=Juan A. |last2=Lozano|accessdate=May 19, 2018|work=[[Associated Press]]|date=May 19, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180520124154/https://www.apnews.com/e8a26b081e2a4206978f750fcdf20a42/|archive-date=May 20, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BarnesHero\">{{cite news |title=Santa Fe school shooting: Wounded officer John Barnes a 'hero' |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-44213620 |work=[[BBC News]] |accessdate=June 21, 2018 |date=May 22, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612151348/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-44213620 |archive-date=June 12, 2018 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BarnesNYT\">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/21/us/santa-fe-officer-wounded-joh